    badge: "new",
    overview: "The Wausau Finance Committee denied a tax recovery claim related to ongoing Greenwood Hills litigation, approved several airport ground lease transfers, and postponed decisions on a national opioid settlement and lead service line funding. The committee also approved 2025 carryover funds and budget transfers while reviewing positive general fund financial results showing a $540,000 surplus.",
